description:
The Feeble Files (c) Adventure Soft

Take on the role of galaxy-saving rebel as you help Feeble overcome the vile OmniBrain, ruler of everything.
An epic space adventure which sees you getting thrown in the galaxy&amp;#039;s toughest prison, dressing up in women&amp;#039;s clothes, and being interrogated by rubber clad space vixens - but not in that order.

Four CDs worth of classic adventuring, featuring SVGA Silicon Graphics rendered animation, 16-bit stereo sound, and hour upon hour of compelling gameplay.

This is the four (4) CD original version, and was converted to run with ScummVM (since version 0.9.1).

